  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK409">
<l>mēlpiṟantā rāyiṉum kallātār kīḻppiṟantuṅ</l>
<l>kaṟṟā raṉaittilar pāṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The unlearned, though born in a high caste, are not equal in dignity to the learned; though they may have been born in a low caste.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
